// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0026 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 294d9185-fd7d-5693-9319-cb8563fae631

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
